If you love Korean food and Mexican food, then this is the place for you! I mean, galbi beef tacos and pork belly kimchi burritos just sound amazing, and it turns out they taste amazing too!!I also tried their Korean fried chicken in soy and original flavors. They are super crispy & satisfying to eat. I will definitely be back for more wings.Self parking in this plaza may need some luck, especially during weekend nights. But I believe they have valet (as this is K-town).
